  <num>30-905</num>
  <heading>PRIZE STRUCTURE FOR THE DC-4 GAME (§ 30-905)</heading>
  <level>
    <num>905.1.</num>
    <text>Based on a fifty cents (50¢) bet, the prize structure for the DC-4 game shall be as follows:</text>
    <text>Bet Types Payout</text>
    <level>
      <num>(a)</num>
      <text>Straight $2,500.00</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(b)</num>
      <text>Four-Way Box 599.50</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(c)</num>
      <text>Six-Way Box 400.00</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(d)</num>
      <text>Twelve-Way Box 200.00</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(e)</num>
      <text>Twenty-Four Box 100.00</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(f)</num>
      <text>Front Three 250.00</text>
    </level>
    <level>
      <num>(g)</num>
      <text>Back Three 250.00</text>
    </level>
  </level>
  <level>
    <num>905.2.</num>
    <text>Each prize in the DC-4 game shall be paid in a single payment after validation of the ticket.</text>
  </level>
  <level>
    <type>annotations</type>
    <level>
      <heading>SOURCE</heading>
      <text>Final Rulemaking published at 39 DCR 7439, 7458 (October 2, 1992).</text>
    </level>
  </level>
</level>